{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6d2390bd1f","title":"关于派部队制止赣州武斗的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b9899bf3b5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":6,"articleId":"6d2390bd1f"}],"tags":[{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"10aa4b444c","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6d2390bd1f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共中央军委办公厅1967年7月4日编印的《群众来信摘抄》第五十五号上。这期摘抄登载了江西赴京控告团、江西赣州赴京控告分团7月4日的电话汇报，反映赣州武斗情况严重，人员伤亡很大，断粮断水，交通全部堵塞，要求中央立即派部队前往制止武斗。"},{"id":"f7e72eef98","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6d2390bd1f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林彪，当时任中共中央军委副主席。恩来，即周恩来。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9d51bf973c","type":"title","text":"关于派部队制止赣州武斗的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6d2390bd1f"},{"id":"10aa4b444c","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪、恩来同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6d2390bd1f"},{"id":"f7e72eef98","type":"paragraph","text":"赣州问题严重，涉及整个赣南十多县，调一个师去，只能管南昌、吉安、宜春、抚州等处，对赣南鞭长莫及。是否可从广州军区调一个师，至少一个团进驻赣州，将事情办好后仍返广东。此事请先考虑，待面商。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6d2390bd1f"},{"id":"ef768f6d7d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6d2390bd1f"},{"id":"bc1815adff","type":"paragraph","text":"七月六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6d2390bd1f"}],"page":{"id":"bcfc497143","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"6d2390bd1f","start":529,"end":529}}}},"__N_SSG":true}